{"tid":1824022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方流浮山檢懷疑煙花炮竹約值五萬元","createTime":"2020-01-14T06:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T09:52:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":85,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"4e78d9ffec02ef130ab1751b16d2c3e005bf6021","tid":1824022,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方在流浮山檢獲懷疑煙花炮竹，市值約五萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方檢獲的煙花共重約80公斤，包括可發射一百發的大型煙花，每個市值約五至六千元。<br />\n<br />\n元朗警區反黑組探員根據情報，早上在流浮山深灣路一個廢棄的貨櫃箱內，檢獲這批懷疑煙花炮竹，相信由內地偷運來港，用途仍然有待調查，暫時無人被捕。"},{"pid":"80136456ef0b4ba6ad40828609539d758c398d26","tid":1824022,"uid":67454,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"班鄉黑牛屎佬今年應該冇得放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f698005f8749cb9a8520564307b7ed7848700768","tid":1824022,"uid":212626,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JX2arhn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJX2arhn.jpg&h=2c97585d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=376711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376711&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=b1ca711d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376711&h=0a4d1405\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=376711</a>"},{"pid":"861a91ae8cfee3592c6959da35eadaa7b51bc59b","tid":1824022,"uid":15,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"6686035ba256c6692b4e9e8b882b4c599b4f8111","tid":1824022,"uid":59832,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"200煙花手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma